.row.col-lg-8.col-lg-offset-2
    .input-group
        input.form-control(type="text", [(ngModel)]="fullLink", placeholder="Paste a link to shorten it")
        span.input-group-btn
            button.btn.btn-default(type="button", (click)="shorten()", [disabled]="loading") Shorten!
    p(*ngIf="shortLink") your short link: {{shortLink}} 